  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Season the chicken breasts with fish sauce, palm sugar, and crushed black pepper.",
    "Place the chicken breasts in a baking dish and bake for 25-30 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, mix the kaffir lime leaves, ginger, and garlic in a blender until well combined.",
    "Add the fermented tofu and coconut milk to the blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Pour the sauce over the baked chicken breasts and serve hot.",
    "Decorate with kaffir lime leaves and serve with steamed rice or noodles.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy the springy texture and flavor of this fermented dish."
